item.title: Current Role
item.description: Though exact details of my work are proprietary, I can highlight the breadth of the work that I’ve performed at Frontier Communcations. For context, Frontier Communications is a large-sized telecommunications company, aiming to provide fiber and copper service across the United States. In my current role, I worked on the network strategy team, harnessing network data (i.e., bit rate) to push data-driven decisions for the operations teams. Constructed numerous ETL pipelines by leveraging cloud architecture and data engineering practices Compiled disjoint data sets to create a large-scale, standardized database used across network teams Swiftly delivered key analyses of the telecoms network using automated dashboards Developed machine learning models to identify and improve customer experience and service
